snippet.title: Island Of The Damned - Official Trailer [Global Gamejam 2021]
snippet.description:
Take a role of sailor lost on island full of mysteries and secrets. Follow your compass to find all hidden treasures & diaries of the remains, survive day & night on the unknown island and reveal the truth!

Free to play here!
https://struct9.itch.io/island-of-the-damned

The game was developed during the 4-days Global Game Jam 2021 by four guys with love.
